{
  "info": {
    "name": "Piyachok API",
    "description": "NestJS backend for Піячок final-task.\n\n## Setup\n1. Import **Piyachok-API.postman_collection.json** and **Piyachok-API.postman_environment.json**.\n2. Select environment **Piyachok API — Local** (or duplicate for prod).\n3. Edit environment (or collection) variables: **demoEmail**, **demoPassword** — real user credentials.\n4. Run **Auth → Login** (or **Register**) — test scripts save **accessToken** and **refreshToken**.\n5. **Forgot / Reset password:** run **Forgot password** (needs SMTP in backend `.env`). Open the email, copy the `token` query param from the link into variable **passwordResetToken**, set **demoPasswordNew**, then run **Reset password**. Update **demoPassword** to match if you want Login to keep working.\n6. Run **Institutions → List** to auto-fill **institutionId** from the first item (test script).\n\nMultipart: Institutions Create/Update and News Create use **Body → form-data**.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000"
    },
    {
      "key": "accessToken",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "refreshToken",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "institutionId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "reviewId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "newsId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "piyachokId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "userId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "categoryId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "demoEmail",
      "value": "demo@example.com"
    },
    {
      "key": "demoPassword",
      "value": "Password123!"
    },
    {
      "key": "demoPasswordNew",
      "value": "Password123!Reset"
    },
    {
      "key": "passwordResetToken",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Demo User\",\n  \"email\": \"{{demoEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{demoPassword}}\",\n  \"passwordConfirm\": \"{{demoPassword}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "try {",
                  "  const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (j.accessToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', j.accessToken);",
                  "  if (j.refreshToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', j.refreshToken);",
                  "} catch (e) {}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{demoEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{demoPassword}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "try {",
                  "  const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (j.accessToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', j.accessToken);",
                  "  if (j.refreshToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', j.refreshToken);",
                  "} catch (e) {}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Forgot password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/forgot-password",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{demoEmail}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Forgot password responds', () => {",
                  "  pm.expect([200, 400, 500].includes(pm.response.code)).to.be.true;",
                  "});",
                  "try {",
                  "  const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (j.message) { console.log('API message:', j.message); }",
                  "  console.log('If SMTP is configured: open the email, copy the `token` value from the reset link (?token=...) into collection variable `passwordResetToken`, set `demoPasswordNew`, then run Reset password.');",
                  "} catch (e) {}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Reset password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/reset-password",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"{{passwordResetToken}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{demoPasswordNew}}\",\n  \"passwordConfirm\": \"{{demoPasswordNew}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  try {",
                  "    const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (j.message) console.log(j.message);",
                  "  } catch (e) {}",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('passwordResetToken', '');",
                  "  console.log('Optional: set demoPassword to the same value as demoPasswordNew so Login still works.');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Google (credential)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
